<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Miko Amora Komik</title>
    <style>
        * {margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; font-family: sans-serif;}
        body {background: #f8f9fa; color: #333;}
        header {background: #ff6b81; color: white; padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;}
        .komik-list {max-width: 1200px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;}
        .komik-card {background: white; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); text-align: center;}
        .komik-card img {width: 100%; height: 320px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 1rem;}
        footer {text-align: center; padding: 2rem; background: #333; color: white; margin-top: 3rem;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>📚 Miko Amora Komik</h1>
        <p>Tempat baca komik favoritmu yang seru dan unik!</p>
    </header>

    <div class="komik-list">
        <div class="komik-card">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/250x320" alt="Sampul Komik 1">
            <h3>Judul Komik Pertama</h3>
            <p>Deskripsi singkat cerita komikmu</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2026 Miko Amora Komik - Semua Cerita Punya Makna Indah</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
